- [new feature] space. space is type of element. space can contain other space.
on app load root space is loaded. space represented as note just with another background.
on creation of new space user promt for space name. every space has uuid. by doubleclicking
on space: current canvas space is destroyed new is loaded. there is space_stack to go back to
the previous space. space visual representation can be resized, connected with other elements.
